_sText:
Bowsy/Aeniema - Taking full credit for the development of this map. Inspired by DeathBox maps. Made specifically for DeathMatch WarCraft: Source - For my upcomming server.

Please note: If anyone decided to use this map for any of their work, etc or any aspect - please provide credit to me please as I don't mind others using my work/ or if someone would like to work with me.

Haven't touched hammer in 5 years, so this is the result of a quick go at it once again.

P.s. sorry for bad screenshots, it's only a Alpha ;)

Bowsy - [http://exgforums.com/](http://exgforums.com/ "EXG Forums")

Please if possible could I receive feedback for future updates to the map to really nail down on potentially issues with map and improve it.

Not only problems I am looking for but improvements too.

Please note this is the first alpha version and some changes have already been made, such as:

*Removed C4 spawn from CT spawn area.
*Removed Beauty Salon sign's from shop.

Place the .BSP into your Maps folder located in your CStrike folder. Do this whilst CSS is closed, if done whilst CSS is loaded - please make sure to restart CSS for the client to load the map properly into the maplist.

Directory:

D:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\common\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\maps
